{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_21132.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story12","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305301,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":305301}],"nameCenter":"牧野郁美","textCenter":"我要加入玛吉斯之翼。","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameNarration":"牧野郁美","narration":"愿不愿意加入玛吉斯之翼……@我马上给出了答案","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"如果说我并不对由美感到内疚@那肯定是骗人的"},{"narration":"但我的理由并非如此……"},{"narration":"我许下心愿，离梦想更近了一步@而成为魔法少女却会让梦想破灭@我不允许这样的事发生"},{"narration":"我也不想在绝望的尽头散播诅咒"},{"narration":"我不能就这样默默接受@这份宿命……这种命运……"},{"chara":[{"id":100601,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"牧野郁美","nameRight":"美冬","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"你们确定要加入？@这是很重要的选择哦？"},{"chara":[{"id":305301,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"嗯，我明白。@我还是想能得到解放。"},{"chara":[{"id":305301}],"textLeft":"而且……美冬对我很真诚。"},{"chara":[{"id":305301,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"如果你相信所有人能得到解放，@那我就相信你说的那个方法。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":100601,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"…………"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100601,"motion":1}],"textRight":"好的，@欢迎你的加入。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800203,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"友杞由美","textRight":"……[wait:0.8][chara:800203:lipSynch_1]我……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"如果你不清楚怎么做，@还是好好考虑比较好哦。"},{"chara":[{"id":800203}],"textRight":"嗯……"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"牧野郁美","narration":"由美这时看上去很迷茫，但几天后@她也决定加入玛吉斯之翼了","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"只是……她的理由是@“玛吉斯能解放我们”@这让我有些担心……"},{"narration":"说实话……@即便美冬值得相信@也不能轻信玛吉斯那些人……"},{"narration":"她们的确是很厉害啦……"},{"narration":"啊！刚刚说的要保密哦？"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv